CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: NEWTON GOLF: A Sacks Parente Company, is a technology-forward golf company that helps golfers elevate their game. With a growing portfolio of golf products, including putters, golf shafts, golf grips, and other golf-related accessories, the company's innovative accomplishments include the First Vernier Acuity putter, patented Ultra-Low Balance Point (ULBP) putter technology, weight-forward Center-of-Gravity (CG) design, and pioneering ultra-light carbon fiber putter shafts.
